strips

Class Strips

  • java.lang.Object
    • strips.Strips
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Planner

    public class Strips
extends java.lang.Object
implements Planner
    Author:
    Tal Sheinfeld Implementation of STRIPS algorithm according to the given pseudocode: 1. Push goal into the stack 2. Repeat until stack is empty 1. If top is a multi-part goal, push unsatisfied sub-goals into the stack 2. If top is a single unsatisfied goal, 1. Replace it with an action that satisfies the goal 2. Push the action preconditions into the stack 3. If top is an action, 1. Pop it from the stack 2. Simulate its execution and update the knowledge base with its effects 3. Add the action to the plan 4. If top is a satisfied goal, pop it from the stack
